Installation Instructions
=========================


Configuration
-------------

To build the software it is necessary configure with these tools:

  # autoreconf -fi
  # aclocal
  # autoconf
  # automake --add-missing
  # rm -rf autom4te.cache
  
  
Basic Installation
------------------

1. Compile hello with the following command:
  
  ./configure
	
  make

2. Install the binary file.

	make install


The tool will be installed in /usr by default. To change this, edit
the $PREFIX variable in Makefile.


Uninstall
=========

To uninstall just enter:

	make uninstall


Troubleshooting
===============

If there are any problems compiling the program, please write an email
to paulofariias@gmail.com and include your compiling error message.
